Package com.atakmap.android.util

Enum NotificationUtil.GeneralIcon

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<NotificationUtil.GeneralIcon>
      • com.atakmap.android.util.NotificationUtil.GeneralIcon
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<NotificationUtil.GeneralIcon>
    Enclosing class:
    NotificationUtil
    public static enum NotificationUtil.GeneralIcon
extends java.lang.Enum<NotificationUtil.GeneralIcon>
    Plugins using the NotificationUtil will need to use resources that are built into ATAK. This is a general set of icons that can be used as part of a notification. If a plugin does not desire to use one of the preselected icons, you will need to look at the helloworld example for how to use plugin supplied icons.
